The pride of ignorant men elevated by false&#xD;<lb/>
metaphysical speculation would not suffer them&#xD;<lb/>
to consider the Earth only as a small <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
