of the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">corpuscular</hi> system other persons before&#xD;<lb/>
had indeed attempted to show that matter&#xD;<lb/>
