11&#xD;<lb/>
they were endowed with powers of motion and&#xD;<lb/>
that all the varieties of life the forms of things&#xD;<lb/>
were produced by their arrangement and their&#xD;<lb/>
Combinations&#xD;<lb/>
- <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
