and He extended the doctrine of his Master&#xD;<lb/>
He is recorded as a diligent observer He is stated&#xD;<lb/>
by all his Biographers to have been a great&#xD;<lb/>
and indefatigable traveller and one of them&#xD;<lb/>
has made him give an account of his Voyage&#xD;<lb/>
and labours.&#xD;<lb/>
Which account is <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
