                xml:id="pb-15"
                facs="#i15"/>
            <lb/>
13&#xD;<lb/>
The cultivated mathematics whilst passing over&#xD;<lb/>
the public roads with as much success as if&#xD;<lb/>
I had been seated tranquilly in my chamber&#xD;<lb/>
And I believe that no person living can&#xD;<lb/>
