            <lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">properties</hi> of <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">things by numbers</hi> and lines&#xD;<lb/>
I will not even except the priests of <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag27"
                ref="#place_475"
                type="place">
               <name xml:id="tag27" type="place">
          Egypt
        </name>
            </rs>
