               <name xml:id="tag30" type="person">
          Democritus
        </name>
            </rs> added to the system of <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag31"
                ref="#person_906"
                type="person">
               <name xml:id="tag31" type="person">
          Leucippus
        </name>
            </rs> -&#xD;<lb/>
Void space and he supposed that all the agencies&#xD;<lb/>
of the corpuscles composing matter were exerted in&#xD;<lb/>
this space.&#xD;<lb/>
Many opinions were attributed <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
