            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                n="34"
                xml:id="pb-34"
                facs="#i34"/>
            <lb/>
32&#xD;<lb/>
It has been supposed that He had formed&#xD;<lb/>
brilliant and comprehensive for civilizing the&#xD;<lb/>
